OL,3,COne in three councils not confident
OL,4,Cthey can provide basic adult social
OL,5,Ccare
OL,7,FCouncils are losing confidence in
OL,8,Ftheir ability to provide good social
OL,9,Fcare, according to data shared
OL,10,Fexclusively with ITV News. Deputy
OL,11,FPolitical Editor Anushka Asthana
OL,12,Freports.
OL,14,FA deep dive into the crisis engulfing
OL,15,Fadult social care has revealed almost
OL,16,Fa third of councils are no longer
OL,17,Fconfident they can even meet their
OL,18,Fbasic legal duties towards elderly and
OL,19,Fvulnerable residents next year.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G1/13
