OL,7,FResearch from the Local Government
OL,8,FAssociation (LGA), shared exclusively
OL,9,Fwith ITV News, lays bare the scale of
OL,10,Ffear felt by those leading this work in
OL,12,FA survey with dozens of adult social
OL,13,Fcare leads suggests just 8% are very
OL,14,Fconfident about meeting their
OL,15,Fstatutory duties for 2025/26 - down
OL,16,Ffrom 27% when looking ahead towards
OL,17,Fthis year, 2024/25.
