OL,7,FThat means many people in - are
OL,8,Ffailing to get it - with visits either
OL,9,Fbeing cancelled or shortened over many
OL,10,Fyears.
OL,12,FThe fears about meeting the legal
OL,13,Frequirements come despite eight out of
OL,14,F10 councils forecasting having to cut
OL,15,Fspending on other community services
OL,16,Fsuch as parks, libraries and leisure
OL,17,Fcentres to try to protect funding.
