OL,7,F89-year-old David Gower - who lives in
OL,8,Fcouncil-run sheltered accommodation in
OL,9,FLuton - says the decline in support
OL,10,Fhas been devastating, plummeting
OL,11,Fstraight down "like the cliffs of
OL,12,FDover".
OL,14,FHe used to get a visit to help him
OL,15,Fshower three times a week - but now
OL,16,Fonly gets that help once a week. Being
OL,17,Ftaken out to the day room to socialise
OL,18,Fhas reduced from two or three times a
OL,19,Fweek to once a month "if I'm lucky".
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G5/13
