OL,7,FHe warns that the reduction in support
OL,8,Fis putting pressure on health services
OL,9,F- as it makes it more likely he will
OL,10,Fdecline to a level that requires NHS
OL,11,Fintervention.
OL,13,FMr Gower, who praised the work of Age
OL,14,FUK, said he wants politicians to work
OL,15,Fcross-party on this.
OL,17,F"We're not dealing with commodity,
OL,18,Fwe're not dealing with a service,
OL,19,Fwe're dealing with life - and life is
OL,20,Fnot cheap," he says.
