OL,7,FLuton Council says it has faced
OL,8,Freduced funding but is committed to
OL,9,Fproviding quality care and will meet
OL,10,FDavid to review his needs, adding: "We
OL,11,Fare very sorry to hear that he is
OL,12,Fdissatisfied with our service and we
OL,13,Fwill do all we can to remedy this."
OL,15,FRecruiting and retaining care workers
OL,16,Fis another huge challenge.
