OL,7,F'You want to spend more time with
OL,8,Fpeople, but you just can't': Julie
OL,9,FSansom told ITV News the lack of
OL,10,Fresources has made it 'stressful' to
OL,11,Fgive people even a basic level of care
OL,13,FJulie Sansom, a domiciliary care
OL,14,Fworker in Nottingham, has joined the
OL,15,FHomecare Workers' Group for support as
OL,16,Fpressures mount with zero hour
OL,17,Fcontracts, no sick pay and
OL,18,Fincreasingly vulnerable clients.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G8/13
