OL,7,F"As well as giving medication, using
OL,8,Fequipment, you're also like a social
OL,9,Fworker and a psychiatrist at times,"
OL,10,Fsays Ms Sansom, who sees on average
OL,11,Ften clients per shift.
OL,13,F"They can get very upset and very
OL,14,Femotional and it would be nice to be
OL,15,Fable to spend time with that person -
OL,16,Fbut you just can't because you have,
OL,17,Fhowever long it is that slot, and then
OL,18,Fyou've got to go to the next one."
