OL,7,FIn the report - ten years on - the LGA
OL,8,Fmade clear councillors believe the
OL,9,Flegislation is still correct to codify
OL,10,Fa set of principles - but makes clear
OL,11,Fthat there is a strong feeling that
OL,12,Fthe country is collectively falling
OL,13,Fshort in its support for some of it's
OL,14,Fmost vulnerable citizens.
OL,16,FAs well as the funding squeeze - they
OL,17,Fpoint to huge pressures around
OL,18,Frecruiting and retaining staff - and
OL,19,Fcall for urgent financial help.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G    G11/13
